c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> Nike x Jacquemus 2024 春季系列还有哪些库存？ </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024年3月26日</time></div></div></div><h2 class="heading larva //   a-font-primary-bold-xl   ">Nike Air Max：简史</h2><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   ">Air Max 已经问世近 40 年了。 Nike 于 1987 年 3 月 26 日首次推出了这款由 Tinker Hatfield 设计的创新运动鞋。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   ">巴黎蓬皮杜中心为原版 Air Max 的<a href="https://www.nike.com/a/air-max-1-history" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.nike.com/a/air-max-1-history" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">设计提供了灵感</a>。据说，耐克派哈特菲尔德到巴黎寻找灵感，他在蓬皮杜中心的解构设计中找到了灵感——这座建筑本质上是<a rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow" href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=87443X1644751&amp;isjs=1&amp;jv=15.5.0-stackpath&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fculture%2Fproduct-recommendations%2Fnike-air-max-shop-new-release-1235641872%2F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arup.com%2Fprojects%2Fcentre-pompidou&amp;xs=1&amp;xtz=420&amp;xuuid=97d258d1ea76d26342414b1c90411a00&amp;cci=638d5a47e0ad06a97dd4166e9453a2c7" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.arup.com/projects/centre-pompidou" target="_blank">“从里到外”翻转的</a>，所有的机械装置都在外面。哈特菲尔德将这一概念融入到 Air Max 暴露的气泡中。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "> Air Max 还采用突破性的缓震技术，让脚步更加舒适。该鞋款与<a rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow" href="https://www.jdoqocy.com/click-100294847-13067763?sid=BB-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nike.com%2Fw%2Fbest-76m50" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.jdoqocy.com/click-100294847-13067763?sid=BB-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nike.com%2Fw%2Fbest-76m50" target="_blank">Nike Dunk</a> <a rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow" href="https://www.jdoqocy.com/click-100294847-13067763?sid=BB-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nike.co